topic: Movie Workflow Series ("Tv series explorative search")

goals.1: Return the number of seasons and episodes per season of the tv series
goals.2: Get the number of episodes in which the cast members played a role. Who are the most present actors?
goals.3: Check who is the actor who acted in more films while working on "How I met your mother" and who is the actor who participated in more films after the end of the tv series.
goals.4: Compare HIMYM with the tv series "The Office (US)" in terms of number of seasons, episods and cast members.
goals.5: Return how many of the actors who are members of the cast of the tv series have [Kavin Bacon number](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Six_Degrees_of_Kevin_Bacon#:~:text=Kevin%20Bacon%20himself%20has%20a,Bacon%20number%20is%20N%2B1.) equal to 2

1.query: SELECT ?tv_series ?name ?numEpisodes ?numSeasons WHERE { VALUES ?tv_series { wd:Q147235 wd:Q23831 } ?tv_series wdt:P1113 ?numEpisodes ; wdt:P2437 ?numSeasons . ?tv_series sc:name ?name } GROUP BY ?tv_series ?name

2.query: SELECT DISTINCT ?p ?pName ?o ?oName WHERE { wd:Q7757165 ?p ?o. ?p <http://schema.org/name> ?pName . ?o <http://schema.org/name> ?oName . } ORDER BY ?pName

2.query: SELECT ?actor ?actorName COUNT(DISTINCT ?episode) AS ?numEpisodes WHERE { wd:Q147235 wdt:P527/wdt:P527 ?episode . ?episode wdt:P161 ?actor . ?actor <http://schema.org/name> ?actorName . } GROUP BY ?actor ?actorName ORDER BY DESC(?numEpisodes) LIMIT 6

3.narrative: single literal associated to an URI

3.query: SELECT ?s ?sName ?p ?pName WHERE { ?s ?p wd:Q200566 . ?p <http://schema.org/name> ?pName . ?s <http://schema.org/name> ?sName . } ORDER BY ?pName LIMIT 20
SELECT ?film ?filmName WHERE { ?film wdt:P161 wd:Q200566 ; wdt:P31 wd:Q11424 . ?film <http://schema.org/name> ?filmName . } ORDER BY ?filmName

SELECT ?actor ?actorName COUNT(DISTINCT ?film) AS ?numFilms WHERE { wd:Q147235 wdt:P161 ?actor . ?film wdt:P31 wd:Q11424 ; wdt:P161 ?actor ; wdt:P577 ?publicationDate . ?actor <http://schema.org/name> ?actorName . FILTER (?publicationDate > "2005-09-19"^^xsd:date AND ?publicationDate < "2014-03-31"^^xsd:date ) } GROUP BY ?actor ?actorName ORDER BY DESC(?numFilms) LIMIT 10

SELECT ?actor ?actorName COUNT(DISTINCT ?film) AS ?numFilms WHERE { wd:Q147235 wdt:P161 ?actor . ?film wdt:P31 wd:Q11424 ; wdt:P161 ?actor ; wdt:P577 ?publicationDate . ?actor <http://schema.org/name> ?actorName . FILTER (?publicationDate > "2014-03-31"^^xsd:date ) } GROUP BY ?actor ?actorName ORDER BY DESC(?numFilms) LIMIT 10

5.query: SELECT DISTINCT ?person ?personName ?personSurname WHERE { ?person wdt:P734 ?surname . ?person <http://schema.org/name> ?personName . ?surname <http://schema.org/name> ?personSurname . FILTER EXISTS{ ?film wdt:P31 wd:Q11424 ; wdt:P161 ?person . } FILTER(REGEX(?personSurname, "Bacon")) } LIMIT 10
